# 3️⃣ Scale Mobile deployment to 0

```yaml
---
- name: Find Mobile Deployment
  shell: >
    oc get deployment -n {{ namespace }} | grep mobile | awk '{print $1}'
  register: mobile_deploy
  ignore_errors: yes

- name: Scale Mobile deployment to 0
  shell: >
    oc scale deployment {{ item }} --replicas=0 -n {{ namespace }}
  loop: "{{ mobile_deploy.stdout_lines }}"
  when: mobile_deploy.stdout != ""
```

