# 11️⃣ MSTR Environment Template

`templates/mstr-env.yaml.j2`

```yaml
apiVersion: cloud.microstrategy.com/v1
kind: MstrEnvironment

metadata:
  name: {{ mstr_env_name }}
  namespace: {{ namespace }}

spec:
  environmentType: {{ environment_type }}
  environmentSize: {{ environment_size }}
  microstrategyVersion: "{{ microstrategy_version }}"

  imageRegistry: {{ image_registry }}

  dnsEntry: {{ dns_entry }}

  ingressController:
    type: istio
    tlsSecretName: {{ tls_secret }}

  persistentVolumeClaimSpecOverrides:
    resources:
      requests:
        storage: {{ storage_size }}
    storageClassName: {{ storage_class }}

  restoreFrom:
    preset: image

  networkPolicies:
    dnsPort: 5353

  volumePermissions:
    enabled: false
```

