# 12️⃣ Create Route

`tasks/route.yml`

```yaml
---
- name: Get CA bundle
  shell: oc get configmap openshift-tls-ca -n {{ namespace }} -o jsonpath='{.data.ca-bundle\.crt}'
  register: ca_bundle

- name: Save CA certificate to file
  copy:
    content: "{{ ca_bundle.stdout }}"
    dest: /tmp/route-ca.crt

- name: Get Istio ingress gateway service
  shell: oc get svc -n {{ namespace }} -l istio=ingressgateway -o jsonpath='{.items[0].metadata.name}'
  register: ingress_service

- name: Create Route
  shell: |
    oc create route reencrypt route-{{ mstr_env_name }} \
      --service={{ ingress_service.stdout }} \
      --hostname={{ dns_entry }} \
      --dest-ca-cert=/tmp/route-ca.crt \
      -n {{ namespace }}
  register: route_create
  ignore_errors: yes

- name: Remove temporary CA file
  file:
    path: /tmp/route-ca.crt
    state: absent
```

