# 13️⃣ Wait Until Environment Ready

`tasks/wait_env.yml`

```yaml
- name: Wait for MSTR environment to be READY
  shell: >
    oc get mstrenvironment {{ mstr_env_name }}
    -n {{ namespace }}
    -o jsonpath='{.status.environmentStatus}'
  register: env_status
  retries: 40
  delay: 30
  until: env_status.stdout == "READY"
```

